rmal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T03:22:10.000Z","msg":"除非你 English native level, 否則唔太建議<br />\n1. SYD 冇job offer唔易nom，分數要求高<br />\n2. 去澳洲讀ug 4年個d學生都牙痛咁聲, 而你得兩年時間<br />\n3. 係SYD畢業後會進入 PR同JOB OFFER 既雞先蛋先兩難局<br />\nrecommendation<br />\n去其他一GRAD 就有NOMINATION 既地方, 如REGIONAL NSW, 其他州<br />\n可以幫你搵下, PM傾"},{"pid":"b24ce3f3e40f327825cf41fd5d44facfdcbba767","tid":1959232,"uid":197583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a9a8af2b1a5881b2cc5ee5394acaa8be8ec4c9e0","tid":1959232,"uid":41958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T16:30:27.000Z","msg":"巴打，想請教下<br />\n<br />\n我29歲，香港讀bachelor and master<br />\n<br />\n7年經驗 technical sales representative <br />\n<br />\n照計歲數+single+bachelor+working experience 已經65分<br />\n<br />\n我細佬係Adelaide ,有PR ,加多15即係80分<br />\n<br />\n爭ielts未考，如果有7就90分<br />\n<br />\n想問問如果80分，甚至90分，想申請491有冇機會?同埋要幾耐先批<br />\n<br />\n另外technical sales係Adelaide 易唔易搵到工?<br />\n<br />\n最後一個問題係想問如果VETASSES 做reference check係咪我未遞form申請491就可以開始apply左先?定係要遞完491form先可以搵vetasses 做skilled skilled assessment"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T03:38:35.000Z","msg":"1. Tech sales 只可走 491 STATE, SA 會nom immediate family member, 細佬應該OK,SA要 +15後85分*<br />\n2. 7年TECH SALES VETASSESS 要減1-3年工作經，留意 <br />\n3. VETASSESS 做完先可以做491<br />\n留意, TECH SALES REP 我做過幾次, 要寫得好清楚你賣既野有幾technical. VETASSESS 睇得好緊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*You must have 75 points (including state nomination points) on the Department of Home Affairs' points test. If your occupation requires offshore applicants to have 85 points (including state nomination points), you will need to meet the 85 points requirements <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.migration.sa.gov.au/skilled-migrants/nomination-process/skilled-nomination-requirements/chain-migration-family-member-in-south-australia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.migration.sa.gov.au%2Fskilled-migrants%2Fnomination-process%2Fskilled-nomination-requirements%2Fchain-migration-family-member-in-south-australia&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfz4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=43867e4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.migration.sa.gov.au/skilled-migrants/nomination-process/skilled-nomination-requirements/chain-migration-family-member-in-south-australia</a>"}]}